# WattZap Savings Command Centre — environment variables
#
# The demo build runs with NO environment variables: it uses an in-memory,
# seeded data layer and cookie sessions. The variables below are consumed
# once the production adapters are enabled (see README "Production wiring").

# --- Supabase (production data + auth + storage) ---
# NEXT_PUBLIC_SUPABASE_URL=https://<project>.supabase.co
# NEXT_PUBLIC_SUPABASE_ANON_KEY=<anon key — safe for browser>
# SUPABASE_SERVICE_ROLE_KEY=<server-only; never expose to the client>

# --- WattZap Coach AI backend (optional; rule-based fallback ships built-in) ---
# ANTHROPIC_API_KEY=<server-only>

# --- Notifications (optional integrations) ---
# WHATSAPP_API_TOKEN=<server-only>
# SMS_GATEWAY_KEY=<server-only>

# --- App ---
# NEXT_PUBLIC_APP_URL=https://app.wattzap.in
